queryResponse.sql:
-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'shipment_state_transitions_agg.first_tendered_week'


-- use existing shipper_parents in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVYW11669665012134_shipper_parents
-- use existing shipper_pod_groups in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV88M1669664129594_shipper_pod_groups
-- use existing shipment_state_transitions_agg in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV0EQ1669665875769_shipment_state_transitions_agg
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "shipper_parents.parent_shipper_name") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN (CASE WHEN "shipments.shipment_count" IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) ELSE 2 END, CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN "shipments.shipment_count" ELSE NULL END DESC, "shipments.shipment_count" DESC, z__pivot_col_rank, "shipper_parents.parent_shipper_name") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "shipment_state_transitions_agg.first_tendered_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipment_state_transitions_agg.first_tendered_week" DESC) AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "shipment_state_transitions_agg.first_tendered_week",
    shipper_parents."PARENT_SHIPPER_NAME"  AS "shipper_parents.parent_shipper_name",
    AVG(( datediff('hour',(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"),(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"))  ) ) AS "shipments.hours_first_on_hold_to_first_tendered_average",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) AND ((datediff('hour',(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"),(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"))/24.0  > 1)) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS count_shipments_scheduled_24_hr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id = shipments.shipper_application_id
INNER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVYW11669665012134_shipper_parents AS shipper_parents ON array_contains(shipper_applications.id, (shipper_parents."SHIPPER_ENTITY_ID_ARRAY"))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV88M1669664129594_shipper_pod_groups AS shipper_pod_groups ON (shipper_pod_groups."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID")=shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV0EQ1669665875769_shipment_state_transitions_agg AS shipment_state_transitions_agg ON shipment_state_transitions_agg.shipment_id=shipments.id
WHERE (shipments.state not in ('canceled','e_submitted') and shipments.is_tonu!='true' and shipments.shipper_application_id != 625 ) AND (shipper_pod_groups."POD_NAME" ) IN ('Pod 1', 'Pod 2', 'Pod 3', 'Pod 4') AND (((( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  )) < (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('minute', 0, DATE_TRUNC('minute', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AND ((( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', -7, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 14, DATEADD('day', -7, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))) <=  (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 5000 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank

-- sql for creating the pivot row totals
SELECT
    shipper_parents."PARENT_SHIPPER_NAME"  AS "shipper_parents.parent_shipper_name",
    AVG(( datediff('hour',(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"),(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"))  ) ) AS "shipments.hours_first_on_hold_to_first_tendered_average",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN ((CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0) AND ((datediff('hour',(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"),(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"))/24.0  > 1)) THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS count_shipments_scheduled_24_hr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id = shipments.shipper_application_id
INNER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVYW11669665012134_shipper_parents AS shipper_parents ON array_contains(shipper_applications.id, (shipper_parents."SHIPPER_ENTITY_ID_ARRAY"))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV88M1669664129594_shipper_pod_groups AS shipper_pod_groups ON (shipper_pod_groups."SHIPPER_APPLICATION_ID")=shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV0EQ1669665875769_shipment_state_transitions_agg AS shipment_state_transitions_agg ON shipment_state_transitions_agg.shipment_id=shipments.id
WHERE (shipments.state not in ('canceled','e_submitted') and shipments.is_tonu!='true' and shipments.shipper_application_id != 625 ) AND (shipper_pod_groups."POD_NAME" ) IN ('Pod 1', 'Pod 2', 'Pod 3', 'Pod 4') AND (((( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  )) < (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('minute', 0, DATE_TRUNC('minute', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AND ((( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  ) >= ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', -7, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))) AND ( shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  ) < ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(DATEADD('day', 14, DATEADD('day', -7, DATE_TRUNC('week', DATE_TRUNC('day', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND ((CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_ON_HOLD_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))) <=  (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(shipment_state_transitions_agg."FIRST_TENDERED_AT"  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)) AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))))
GROUP BY
    1
ORDER BY
    4 DESC
FETCH NEXT 30000 ROWS ONLY
